<br>
If the mob is too high, the Dire Charm resets when you try to charm.<br>
<br>
If the mob is tagged as uncharmable, it uses your ability and the mob will resist (i.e. Sergeant Slate is light blue but cannot be charmed with Dire, hence wasting the ability).<br>
<br>
If the mob CAN be charmed with the ability, it is impossible to resist.  Works fine on Dar knights in Seb, recruits and low level SK's in chardok, walruses in SG, HS mobs, Velk spiders, etc. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87709>Master Rubicant D'Luness - Phantasmist</a><BR>
